  "mainHtml": "<div class=\"mb-6\">\n<nav class=\"flex text-label-sm font-label-sm text-on-surface-variant mb-2\">\n<ol class=\"flex items-center space-x-2\">\n<li><a class=\"hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/\">首页</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-[14px]\">chevron_right</span></li>\n<li class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">供应管理</li>\n</ol>\n</nav>\n<div class=\"flex flex-col xl:flex-row xl:items-end xl:justify-between gap-4\">\n<div>\n<h1 class=\"text-display-lg font-display-lg text-on-surface m-0\">供应管理</h1>\n<p class=\"text-body-md font-body-md text-on-surface-variant mt-1\">统一管理订单外协、供应商交付、扫码回传进度与异常协同，作为平台供应履约总入口。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-3\">\n<button class=\"h-10 px-4 bg-surface-container-lowest border border-outline-variant rounded-lg text-title-sm font-title-sm text-on-surface flex items-center gap-2 hover:bg-surface-container transition-colors shadow-sm\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]\">add_task</span>新建外协任务</button>\n<button class=\"h-10 px-4 bg-primary text-on-primary rounded-lg text-title-sm font-title-sm flex items-center gap-2 hover:bg-primary-container hover:text-on-primary-container transition-colors shadow-sm\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]\">download</span>导出交付日报</button>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-4 gap-6 mb-8\">\n<div class=\"bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl p-5 border border-outline-variant/50 shadow-[0_1px_3px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.1),0_1px_2px_-1px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)]\"><div class=\"flex items-start justify-between mb-4\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-surface-container flex items-center justify-center text-primary\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined\">inventory_2</span></div><span class=\"inline-flex items-center text-label-sm font-label-sm text-primary bg-primary-fixed px-2 py-1 rounded-full\">今日新增 12</span></div><div class=\"text-label-sm font-label-sm text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-wider mb-1\">外协订单池</div><div class=\"text-display-lg font-display-lg text-on-surface leading-none\">186</div><p class=\"text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mt-3\">覆盖机加工、钣金、热处理与表面处理协同订单。</p></div>\n<div class=\"bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl p-5 border border-outline-variant/50 shadow-[0_1px_3px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.1),0_1px_2px_-1px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)]\"><div class=\"flex items-start justify-between mb-4\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-surface-container flex items-center justify-center text-primary\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined\">local_shipping</span></div><span class=\"inline-flex items-center text-label-sm font-label-sm text-secondary bg-secondary-fixed px-2 py-1 rounded-full\">在途 74</span></div><div class=\"text-label-sm font-label-sm text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-wider mb-1\">交付执行中</div><div class=\"text-display-lg font-display-lg text-on-surface leading-none\">92</div><p class=\"text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mt-3\">供应商正在执行的工单、发货与收货节点实时汇总。</p></div>\n<div class=\"bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl p-5 border border-outline-variant/50 shadow-[0_1px_3px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.1),0_1px_2px_-1px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)]\"><div class=\"flex items-start justify-between mb-4\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-surface-container flex items-center justify-center text-primary\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined\">qr_code_scanner</span></div><span class=\"inline-flex items-center text-label-sm font-label-sm text-primary bg-primary-fixed px-2 py-1 rounded-full\">回传率 92%</span></div><div class=\"text-label-sm font-label-sm text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-wider mb-1\">扫码进度回传</div><div class=\"text-display-lg font-display-lg text-on-surface leading-none\">418</div><p class=\"text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mt-3\">开工、首件、巡检、完工、发货等节点已扫码上传。</p></div>\n<div class=\"bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl p-5 border border-outline-variant/50 shadow-[0_1px_3px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.1),0_1px_2px_-1px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)]\"><div class=\"flex items-start justify-between mb-4\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-surface-container flex items-center justify-center text-primary\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined\">warning</span></div><span class=\"inline-flex items-center text-label-sm font-label-sm text-on-error-container bg-error-container px-2 py-1 rounded-full\">需处理 11</span></div><div class=\"text-label-sm font-label-sm text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-wider mb-1\">延期与异常预警</div><div class=\"text-display-lg font-display-lg text-on-surface leading-none\">11</div><p class=\"text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mt-3\">交期偏移、质量异常、缺件和未扫码节点会在这里集中预警。</p></div>\n</div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 xl:grid-cols-12 gap-6 mb-8\">\n<section class=\"xl:col-span-7 bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/50 shadow-[0_1px_3px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.1),0_1px_2px_-1px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)] p-6\">\n<div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-5\"><div><h3 class=\"text-title-sm font-title-sm text-on-surface\">外协订单协同看板</h3><p class=\"text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mt-1\">按订单当前阶段统一管理外协下发、生产执行、发货与收货确认。</p></div><button class=\"px-3 h-9 rounded-lg border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-lowest text-body-md text-on-surface hover:bg-surface-container transition-colors\">调整优先级</button></div>\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-5\">\n<div class=\"rounded-xl bg-surface-container-low p-5 border border-outline-variant/40\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-3\"><div class=\"font-semibold text-on-surface\">待下发外协</div><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-error-container text-on-error-container text-label-sm\">28</span></div><div class=\"space-y-3 text-body-md\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span>壳体五轴精加工</span><span class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">8 单</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span>钣金折弯与焊接</span><span class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">11 单</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span>阳极氧化与喷砂</span><span class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">9 单</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"rounded-xl bg-surface-container-low p-5 border border-outline-variant/40\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-3\"><div class=\"font-semibold text-on-surface\">生产执行中</div><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-primary-fixed text-on-primary-fixed-variant text-label-sm\">92</span></div><div class=\"space-y-3 text-body-md\"><div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-1\"><span>CNC 批量加工</span><span class=\"font-semibold text-on-surface\">63%</span></div><div class=\"h-2 rounded-full bg-surface-container-high overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"h-full w-[63%] bg-primary rounded-full\"></div></div></div><div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-1\"><span>表面处理排程</span><span class=\"font-semibold text-on-surface\">48%</span></div><div class=\"h-2 rounded-full bg-surface-container-high overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"h-full w-[48%] bg-secondary rounded-full\"></div></div></div><div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-1\"><span>装配与终检</span><span class=\"font-semibold text-on-surface\">35%</span></div><div class=\"h-2 rounded-full bg-surface-container-high overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"h-full w-[35%] bg-tertiary rounded-full\"></div></div></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"rounded-xl bg-surface-container-low p-5 border border-outline-variant/40\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-3\"><div class=\"font-semibold text-on-surface\">待发货 / 待收货</div><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-secondary-fixed text-on-secondary-fixed text-label-sm\">26</span></div><div class=\"space-y-3 text-body-md text-on-surface-variant\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span>待供应商发货</span><span class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">17</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span>待仓库签收</span><span class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">6</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span>待IQC检验</span><span class=\"text-on-surface font-semibold\">3</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"rounded-xl bg-surface-container-low p-5 border border-outline-variant/40\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-3\"><div class=\"font-semibold text-on-surface\">供应协同建议</div><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-tertiary-fixed text-tertiary text-label-sm\">AI建议</span></div><div class=\"space-y-3 text-body-md text-on-surface-variant\"><div class=\"flex gap-3\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-primary\">check_circle</span><span>把阳极氧化订单合并到同一供应商批次，降低往返物流成本。</span></div><div class=\"flex gap-3\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-primary\">check_circle</span><span>对 5 家未扫码的供应商开启自动提醒，优先催回首件与巡检节点。</span></div><div class=\"flex gap-3\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-primary\">check_circle</span><span>延期风险订单建议提前触发客服与采购双人协同。</span></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"xl:col-span-5 space-y-6\">\n<div class=\"bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/50 shadow-[0_1px_3px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.1),0_1px_2px_-1px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)] p-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-4\"><div><h3 class=\"text-title-sm font-title-sm text-on-surface\">异常与待办</h3><p class=\"text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mt-1\">把延期、缺件、质检异常和未回传节点集中处理。</p></div><span class=\"px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-error-container text-on-error-container text-label-sm font-label-sm\">优先级已排序</span></div><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"rounded-xl bg-surface-container-low p-4 border border-outline-variant/40\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\"><div class=\"font-semibold text-on-surface\">主轴座批量件</div><span class=\"text-label-sm text-on-surface-variant\">交期延后 2 天</span></div><div class=\"text-body-md text-on-surface-variant\">供应商：昆山精工 · 原因：热处理排程拥堵</div><div class=\"mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-error-container text-on-error-container text-body-md\">延期申请</span><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-surface-container-high text-body-md\">需客户同步</span></div></div><div class=\"rounded-xl bg-surface-container-low p-4 border border-outline-variant/40\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\"><div class=\"font-semibold text-on-surface\">机器人支架总成</div><span class=\"text-label-sm text-on-surface-variant\">缺少巡检扫码</span></div><div class=\"text-body-md text-on-surface-variant\">供应商：宁波五轴中心 · 当前已开工但未上传巡检节点。</div><div class=\"mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-primary-fixed text-on-primary-fixed-variant text-body-md\">催回扫码</span><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-surface-container-high text-body-md\">自动提醒已发送</span></div></div><div class=\"rounded-xl bg-surface-container-low p-4 border border-outline-variant/40\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\"><div class=\"font-semibold text-on-surface\">铝合金壳体</div><span class=\"text-label-sm text-on-surface-variant\">IQC 待判定</span></div><div class=\"text-body-md text-on-surface-variant\">仓库已签收，质检报告与批次标识不一致，需要复核。</div><div class=\"mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-tertiary-fixed text-tertiary text-body-md\">质量异常</span><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-surface-container-high text-body-md\">待供应商补件</span></div></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/50 shadow-[0_1px_3px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.1),0_1px_2px_-1px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)] p-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-4\"><h3 class=\"text-title-sm font-title-sm text-on-surface\">扫码上传机制</h3><span class=\"text-label-sm text-on-surface-variant\">供应商履约标准</span></div><div class=\"space-y-4 text-body-md\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-0.5 material-symbols-outlined text-primary\">qr_code_scanner</span><div><div class=\"text-on-surface font-medium\">生产节点扫码</div><div class=\"text-on-surface-variant\">开工、首件、巡检、完工、发货五个节点必须扫码回传。</div></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-0.5 material-symbols-outlined text-primary\">photo_camera</span><div><div class=\"text-on-surface font-medium\">图片与附件佐证</div><div class=\"text-on-surface-variant\">关键节点需附现场图片、检验单或物流单据。</div></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-0.5 material-symbols-outlined text-primary\">notifications_active</span><div><div class=\"text-on-surface font-medium\">超时自动提醒</div><div class=\"text-on-surface-variant\">超 4 小时未上传节点自动提醒，超 12 小时升级到平台运营。</div></div></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div><section class=\"bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/50 shadow-[0_1px_3px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.1),0_1px_2px_-1px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)] overflow-hidden mb-8\"><div class=\"p-4 border-b border-outline-variant/50 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between gap-3 bg-surface-bright\"><div><h3 class=\"text-title-sm font-title-sm text-on-surface\">本周交付总览</h3><p class=\"text-body-md text-on-surface-variant mt-1\">快速查看重点外协订单、当前扫码节点、预计交付和异常状态。</p></div><div class=\"flex gap-2\"><button class=\"p-2 text-on-surface-variant hover:bg-surface-container rounded transition-colors border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-lowest\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]\">filter_list</span></button><button class=\"h-10 px-4 bg-primary text-on-primary rounded-lg text-title-sm font-title-sm flex items-center gap-2 hover:bg-primary-container hover:text-on-primary-container transition-colors shadow-sm\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]\">route</span>查看全部协同订单</button></div></div><div class=\"overflow-x-auto w-full\"><table class=\"w-full text-left border-collapse\"><thead><tr class=\"bg-surface-container-low border-b border-outline-variant/50\"><th class=\"px-6 py-3 text-label-sm font-label-sm text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-wider\">订单 / 工序</th><th class=\"px-6 py-3 text-label-sm font-label-sm text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-wider\">供应商</th><th class=\"px-6 py-3 text-label-sm font-label-sm text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-wider\">当前节点</th><th class=\"px-6 py-3 text-label-sm font-label-sm text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-wider\">扫码回传</th><th class=\"px-6 py-3 text-label-sm font-label-sm text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-wider text-right\">预计交付</th><th class=\"px-6 py-3 text-label-sm font-label-sm text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-wider text-center\">状态</th></tr></thead><tbody class=\"divide-y divide-outline-variant/30 bg-surface-container-lowest\"><tr class=\"hover:bg-surface-container/50 transition-colors\"><td class=\"px-6 py-4\"><div class=\"font-medium text-on-surface\">PO-240701 / 主轴座五轴精加工</div><div class=\"text-mono-data text-on-surface-variant text-[11px]\">来源：平台订单 SO-88104</div></td><td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-on-surface\">昆山精工</td><td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-on-surface\">首件检验</td><td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-on-surface\">已上传首件图 + 检验单</td><td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-right text-mono-data text-on-surface\">07-08 16:00</td><td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-center\"><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-primary-fixed text-on-primary-fixed-variant text-[11px] font-medium\">正常</span></td></tr><tr class=\"hover:bg-surface-container/50 transition-colors\"><td class=\"px-6 py-4\"><div class=\"font-medium text-on-surface\">PO-240688 / 铝壳阳极氧化</div><div class=\"text-mono-data text-on-surface-variant text-[11px]\">来源：RFQ 中标批次 RFQ-3226</div></td><td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-on-surface\">苏州表处中心</td><td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-on-surface\">表面处理排程</td><td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-on-surface\">待上传巡检节点</td><td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-right text-mono-data text-on-surface\">07-07 19:30</td><td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-center\"><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-error-container text-on-error-container text-[11px] font-medium\">预警</span></td></tr><tr class=\"hover:bg-surface-container/50 transition-colors\"><td class=\"px-6 py-4\"><div class=\"font-medium text-on-surface\">PO-240672 / 机器人支架焊接总成</div><div class=\"text-mono-data text-on-surface-variant text-[11px]\">来源：MES 外协补工单 WO-5412</div></td><td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-on-surface\">宁波五轴中心</td><td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-on-surface\">生产执行中</td><td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-on-surface\">已开工，巡检未扫码</td><td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-right text-mono-data text-on-surface\">07-09 12:00</td><td class=\"px-6 py-4 text-center\"><span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-tertiary-fixed text-tertiary text-[11px] font-medium\">待跟进</span></td></tr></tbody></table></div></section>"
